snippet.title: RAID: Shadow Legends | Get Ready To Raid (Official Commercial)
snippet.description:
Don your armor, grab your sword, and rally your courage. It’s time to raid! 
RAID: Shadow Legends for free on all devices! 

Download and Play → https://plrm.info/3OAqN5Z

Build a fearsome team from over 300 mighty Champions. Customize them your way and challenge menacing bosses and players from across the world. 

Answer the call of the Arbiter!

Join our Community on:
Facebook → https://plrm.info/3UB0rB3
X (formerly Twitter) → https://plrm.info/twitter
Discord → https://plrm.info/discord

#RaidShadowLegends
